        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/43.13549933241229_-2.165234685311849"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/2"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Endogenous and Exogenous. The Urdapilleta online Store delivers a wide range of products, including ham, shoulder, loin, txorizo, cured chorizo, fresh chorizo, txistorra, lukainka, salchichón, pate, and pancetta, among other products. The innovation is related to New products, New processes and New marketing strategies. The land use systems involved are Grassland. The local assets include Natural, social and cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


