        <ontology:hasDescription>The average per capita income (EUR/year) [Province] is 17631. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Province] is 21774.4. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 6.20%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 43.80%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Province] is 49.90%. The per capita income (EUR/year) [Region] is 21458. The total Gross Value Added (GVA) (EUR million/year) [Region] is 65185. The primary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 0.90%. The secondary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 29.90%. The tertiary sector share of total GVA/year [Region] is 69.20%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
